text: Trails of the Golden West is a 1931 American Western film directed by Leander De Cordova and starring Jay Wilsey, Wanda Hawley and Tom London.Rainey p.163 ==Cast== * Jay Wilsey * Wanda Hawley * Tom London * George Reed * Horace B.
